name: Arigatou Collecteru-chan (From Tezos Maneki-neko)
description:
Someone asked me what my name mean?
I said, Fauzi means lucky. 

2 years ago when I traveled to japan I accidentally lost in Gotokuji Temple. a place where Maneki Nekko or Beckoning cat was born. the atmosphere feels familiar to me and I found hundreds of maneki-nekko are placed at the side of the temple. I dreamed of this place before..

the winds come to me like a whisper somewhat it called my name. after that mysterious event every time i come to the shrine I picked Omikuji (fortunes paper) i always got Golden Luck. it's a spiritual journey for me. and after that I always felt lucky, even I had a bad day. i know a good time will come.

I made this a token of my gratitude to all collectors. I hope this brings you all good fortune as I had before. 

thank you, Arigatou gozaimashita
